#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:3001
msgid "Preparing ubuntu-drivers..."
msgstr ""

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:4001
msgid "Connecting..."
msgstr "袠褍谐芯薪写 泻訒薪褘薪..."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:5001
msgid "Connection failed."
msgstr ""

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:6001
msgid "Connected."
msgstr ""

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:7001
msgid "Restart to Continue"
msgstr "袧訒褍訒谐訒泄 斜邪懈褍 泻訒薪 邪写邪褉写写訒褉 泻訒薪褘薪訒薪"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. This is used as a window title.
#: ../ubiquity.templates:8001
msgid "Install and Migrate Users, Jackjump.com"
msgstr "袩邪泄写邪谐忙薪忙谐褌褘 忙褉忙胁忙褉褘薪 忙屑忙 褉邪懈胁褘薪, Jackjump.com"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:9001
msgid "Install and Migrate Users (OEM mode, for manufacturers only)"
msgstr "袩邪泄写邪谐忙薪忙谐褌褘 忙褉忙胁忙褉褘薪 忙屑忙 褉邪懈胁褘薪 (OEM 褉械卸懈屑, 訒褉屑訒褋褌 泻褍褋訒谐訒薪)"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:10001
msgid ""
"You are installing in system manufacturer mode. Please enter a unique name "
"for this batch of systems. This name will be saved on the installed system "
"and can be used to help with bug reports."
msgstr ""
"袛褘 褉邪胁蟹訒褉褋褌邪泄 褋懈褋褌械屑訒 褋訒胁訒褉褘薪 泻褍褋訒写卸褘 褉械卸懈屑褘. 袧褘褎褎褘褋 褍薪懈泻邪谢芯薪 薪芯屑 邪褑褘 "
"褋懈褋褌械屑訒泄褘 訒屑斜褘褉写訒薪. 袗褑褘 薪芯屑 褍褘写蟹訒薪懈 褎褘褋褌 褋懈褋褌械屑訒泄褘. 袪訒写褘写褌褘 芯褌褔械褌褘 斜邪泻褍褋褘薪褘谢 "
"褏邪泄邪写 懈褋写蟹訒薪懈褋."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. RELEASE is a variable substituted into this string, and may be 'Linux Mint'
#. MEDIUM is a variable substituted into this string, and may be 'CD'
#: ../ubiquity.templates:11001
msgid ""
"You can try ${RELEASE} without making any changes to your computer, directly "
"from this ${MEDIUM}."
msgstr ""
"袛訒 斜芯薪 褍 褎械薪邪泄 ${RELEASE} 訒薪訒 懈胁褘薪写蟹懈薪訒写褌訒泄 写訒 泻芯屑锌褜褞褌械褉褘谢,  泻芯屑泻芯屑屑訒 "
"${MEDIUM}-訒泄."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. RELEASE is a variable substituted into this string, and may be 'Linux Mint'
#: ../ubiquity.templates:11001
msgid ""
"Or if you're ready, you can install ${RELEASE} alongside (or instead of) "
"your current operating system.  This shouldn't take too long."
msgstr ""
"袣訒薪訒 褌邪, 泻訒写 褑訒褌褌訒 写訒, 褍訒写 写訒 斜芯薪 褍 褋訒胁訒褉褘薪 ${RELEASE} 写訒 薪褘褉褘 褋懈褋褌械屑訒泄褘 褑褍褉 "
"(訒胁懈 泄訒 斜訒褋褌褘). 校褘泄 斜懈褉訒 褉訒褋褌訒谐 薪訒  斜邪褏邪褉写蟹 泻忙薪写蟹褘薪懈褋."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. RELEASE is a variable substituted into this string, and may be 'Linux Mint'
#: ../ubiquity.templates:12001
msgid "Try ${RELEASE}"
msgstr "肖械薪褘薪 ${RELEASE}"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. RELEASE is a variable substituted into this string, and may be 'Linux Mint'
#: ../ubiquity.templates:13001
msgid "Install ${RELEASE}"
msgstr "小訒胁訒褉褘薪 ${RELEASE}"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:14001
msgid ""
"You may wish to read the <a href=\"release-notes\">release notes</a> or <a "
"href=\"update\">update this installer</a>."
msgstr ""
"袛訒 斜芯薪 褍 斜邪褎訒褉褋褘薪 <a href=\"release-notes\">褉邪褍邪谐褗写褘 褎懈锌锌邪懈薪訒谐褌訒</a> 泻訒薪訒 褌邪 "
"<a href=\"update\">邪薪訒褍訒谐 泻訒薪褘薪 邪褑褘 褋訒胁訒褉褘薪褘 锌褉芯谐褉邪屑屑訒</a>."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:15001
msgid "You may wish to read the <a href=\"release-notes\">release notes</a>."
msgstr "袛訒 斜芯薪 褍 斜邪褎訒褉褋褘薪 <a href=\"release-notes\">褉邪褍邪谐褗写褘 褎懈锌锌邪懈薪訒谐褌訒</a>."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:16001
msgid "You may wish to <a href=\"update\">update this installer</a>."
msgstr "袛訒 斜芯薪 褍 <a href=\"update\">邪薪訒褍訒谐 泻訒薪褘薪 邪褑褘 褋訒胁訒褉褘薪褘 锌褉芯谐褉邪屑屑訒</a>."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:17001
msgid "Where are you?"
msgstr "袧褘褉 泻訒屑 写訒?"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:18001
msgid "Keyboard layout"
msgstr "袣谢邪胁懈邪褌褍褉訒泄褘 褉邪胁訒褉写"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:19001
msgid "Choose your keyboard layout:"
msgstr "小訒胁蟹邪褉 泻谢邪胁懈邪褌褍褉訒泄褘 褉邪胁蟹邪褉写:"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:20001
msgid "Type here to test your keyboard"
msgstr "袠褋褌褘 薪褘褎褎褘褋 邪屑 訒屑訒 斜邪褋谐邪褉写 泻谢邪胁懈邪褌褍褉訒"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:21001
msgid "Detect Keyboard Layout"
msgstr "袪邪斜訒褉訒谐 泻訒 泻谢邪胁懈邪褌褍褉訒泄褘 褉邪胁訒褉写"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:22001
msgid "Detect Keyboard Layout..."
msgstr "袘邪蟹芯薪褘薪 泻谢邪胁懈邪褌褍褉訒泄褘 褉邪胁訒褉写..."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:23001
msgid "Please press one of the following keys:"
msgstr "袧褘褏褏訒褑 邪褑褘 泻褗薪芯锌泻訒褌訒泄 褋訒 懈褍褘谢"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:24001
msgid "Is the following key present on your keyboard?"
msgstr "袠褋 邪褑褘 泻褗薪芯锌泻訒 写訒 泻谢邪胁懈邪褌褍褉訒泄褘谢?"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:25001
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr "效懈 写訒?"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:26001
msgid "Your name:"
msgstr "袛訒 薪芯屑:"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:27001
msgid "Pick a username:"
msgstr "袪邪胁蟹邪褉 薪芯屑:"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:28001
msgid ""
"&lt;small&gt;If more than one person will use this computer, you can set up "
"multiple accounts after installation.&lt;/small&gt;"
msgstr ""

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:29001
msgid "Must start with a lower-case letter."
msgstr "肖褘褋褌 褏褗褍邪屑訒 褑訒褍邪 谐褘褑褑褘谢 写邪屑谐褗訒."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:30001
msgid "May only contain lower-case letters, digits, hyphens, and underscores."
msgstr ""
"啸褗褍邪屑訒 褍邪 訒褉屑訒褋褌 谐褘褑褑褘谢 写邪屑谐褗褗訒褌訒泄, 薪褘屑訒褑褘 薪褘褋訒薪褌褌訒泄, 写械褎懈褋褌訒泄 訒屑訒 褏邪褏褏 "
"泻訒薪褘薪褘 褋懈屑胁芯谢褌訒泄."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:31001
msgid "Skip"
msgstr "袪邪褍邪写蟹褘薪"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:32001
msgid "Choose a password:"
msgstr "袪邪胁蟹邪褉 锌邪褉芯谢:"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:33001
msgid ""
"&lt;small&gt;Enter the same password twice, so that it can be checked for "
"typing errors.&lt;/small&gt;"
msgstr ""

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:34001
msgid "Password"
msgstr "袩邪褉芯谢"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:35001
msgid "Confirm password"
msgstr "小褎懈写邪褉 泻訒薪 锌邪褉芯谢"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:36001
msgid "Confirm your password:"
msgstr "小褎懈写邪褉 泻訒薪 写訒 锌邪褉芯谢:"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:37001
msgid "Your computer's name:"
msgstr "袛訒 泻芯屑锌褜褞褌械褉褘 薪芯屑:"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:38001
msgid "The name it uses when it talks to other computers."
msgstr "袧芯屑, 懈薪薪訒 泻芯屑锌褜褞褌械褉褌懈屑訒 斜邪褋褌写蟹懈薪邪写 泻訒薪褘薪訒薪"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:39001
msgid "Must be between 1 and 63 characters long."
msgstr "袡訒 写訒褉谐褗 褏褗褍邪屑訒 褍邪 1 写邪屑谐褗訒泄訒 63-屑訒"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:40001
msgid "May only contain letters, digits, hyphens, and dots."
msgstr "啸褗褍邪屑訒 褍邪 訒褉屑訒褋褌 写邪屑谐褗褗訒褌訒泄, 薪褘屑訒褑褘 薪褘褋訒薪褌褌訒泄, 写械褎懈褋褌訒泄 訒屑訒 褌訒锌锌褌懈屑訒."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:41001
msgid "May not start or end with a hyphen."
msgstr "袦邪 褏褗褍邪屑訒 斜邪懈写邪泄邪 泻訒薪訒 褌邪 訒褏褏訒褋褌 泻訒薪邪 写械褎懈褋訒泄."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:42001
msgid "May not start or end with a dot, or contain the sequence \"..\"."
msgstr ""
"袦邪 褏褗褍邪屑訒 斜邪懈写邪泄邪 褌訒锌锌訒泄, 訒褏褏訒褋褌 泻訒薪邪 褌訒锌锌訒泄 泻訒薪訒 褌邪 褍邪 写褘褍褍訒 褌訒锌锌懈屑訒 "
"褎訒写褎訒写褘谢 (\"..\")."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:43001
msgid "You are running in debugging mode. Do not use a valuable password!"
msgstr "小懈褋褌械屑訒 泻褍褋褘 褉訒胁写蟹 泻訒薪褘薪褘 褉械卸懈屑褘. 袦邪 锌邪泄写邪 泻訒 邪褏褋写卸懈邪谐 锌邪褉芯谢褌訒泄."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:44001 ../ubiquity.templates:368001
msgid "Passwords do not match"
msgstr "袩邪褉芯谢褌訒 訒屑褏褍褘褏芯薪 薪械 褋褌褘"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:45001 ../ubiquity.templates:369001
msgid "Short password"
msgstr "訑谐訒褉 褑褘斜褘褉 锌邪褉芯谢"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:46001 ../ubiquity.templates:370001
msgid "Weak password"
msgstr "訑写褘褏 锌邪褉芯谢"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:47001 ../ubiquity.templates:371001
msgid "Fair password"
msgstr "袛蟹訒斜訒褏 锌邪褉芯谢"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:48001 ../ubiquity.templates:372001
msgid "Good password"
msgstr "啸芯褉蟹 锌邪褉芯谢"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:49001 ../ubiquity.templates:373001
msgid "Strong password"
msgstr "孝褘薪谐 褏芯褉蟹 锌邪褉芯谢"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:50001
msgid "Log in automatically"
msgstr "啸訒写邪褉褏邪泄谐訒泄訒 斜邪褏懈蟹褘薪 褋懈褋褌械屑訒屑訒"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:51001
msgid "Require my password to log in"
msgstr "袩邪褉芯谢 写芯屑褘薪 褋懈褋褌械屑訒屑訒 斜邪褏懈蟹褘薪訒薪"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:52001
msgid "Installation type"
msgstr "小訒胁訒褉褘薪褘 褏褍褘蟹"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:53001
msgid "Install drive may not be copy drive"
msgstr "忙胁忙褉忙薪 写懈褋泻 谐忙薪忙薪 懈褋 忙屑忙 屑邪 褍邪 泻芯锌懈 写懈褋泻"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:53001
msgid ""
"An error occurred because install drive and copy drive are the same drive. "
"Please select distinct drives to proceed."
msgstr ""
"袪忙写褘写 忙褉褑褘写, 褍褘屑忙薪 忙屑忙 忙胁忙褉忙薪 写懈褋泻 忙屑忙 泻芯锌懈褉谐忙薪忙薪 写懈褋泻 褋褌褘 懈褍 写懈褋泻. "
"袛忙 褏芯褉蟹忙褏忙泄, 褉邪胁蟹邪褉 褏懈褑忙薪 写懈褋泻褌忙, 褑忙屑忙泄 写邪褉写写忙褉 褑忙褍邪泄."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:54001
msgid "Install drive is BitLocker encrypted"
msgstr "脝胁忙褉褘薪 写懈褋泻 褍 BitLocker 褕懈褎褉谐芯薪写"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:54001
msgid ""
"An error occurred because BitLocker encryption was not disabled on install "
"drive beforehand. Please decrypt it before proceeding."
msgstr ""
"袪忙写褘写 忙褉褑褘写, 褍褘屑忙薪 忙屑忙 BitLocker-褘 褕懈褎褉写蟹懈薪邪写 褉邪蟹写忙褉 薪忙 褍褘写 忙褏谐忙写 忙胁忙褉忙薪 "
"写懈褋泻褘谢. 袛忙 褏芯褉蟹忙褏忙泄, 褉邪褎褘褋褋 忙泄, 褑邪谢褘薪屑忙 写邪褉写写忙褉 薪忙 邪褑忙褍邪泄, 褍忙写屑忙."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:55001
msgid "Please select a valid install drive"
msgstr "袛忙 褏芯褉蟹忙褏忙泄, 褉邪胁蟹邪褉 褉邪褋褌 忙胁忙褉忙薪 写懈褋泻"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:55001
msgid "A valid install drive must be selected in order to proceed."
msgstr ""
"笑忙屑忙泄 写邪褉写写忙褉 褑忙褍忙屑, 褍褘泄 褌褘褏褏忙泄 褏褗褍邪屑忙 忙胁蟹忙褉褋褌 忙褉褑忙褍邪 褉邪褋褌 忙胁忙褉忙薪 写懈褋泻."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:56001
msgid "Copy drive is BitLocker encrypted"
msgstr "袣芯锌懈 写懈褋泻 褍 BitLocker 褕懈褎褉谐芯薪写"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:56001
msgid ""
"An error occurred because BitLocker encryption was not disabled on copy "
"drive beforehand. Please decrypt it before proceeding."
msgstr ""
"袪忙写褘写 忙褉褑褘写, 褍褘屑忙薪 忙屑忙 BitLocker-褘 褕懈褎褉写蟹懈薪邪写 褉邪蟹胁忙谢谐褗邪褍 薪忙 褍褘写 忙褏谐忙写 "
"泻芯锌懈泄褘 写懈褋泻褘谢. 袛忙 褏芯褉蟹忙褏忙泄, 褉邪褎褘褋褋 忙泄, 褑邪谢褘薪屑忙 写邪褉写写忙褉 薪忙 邪褑忙褍邪泄, 褍忙写屑忙."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:57001
msgid "Copy drive did not mount"
msgstr "袣芯锌懈 写懈褋泻 薪忙 屑芯薪褌邪卸谐芯薪写 忙褉褑褘写"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../ubiquity.templates:57001
msgid ""
"The copy drive has an issue: its filesystem is not supported or something "
"else is making it unable to mount."
msgstr ""
